 the consumer lending segment primarily includes residential mortgages home equity loans and automobile loans the commercial lending segment primarily includes floating rate and adjustable rate commercial and industrial loans as well as fixed rate owner occupied and commercial real estate loans the investment management segment includes the companys investments in various types of securities as of july   the bank had  branch locations serving northern and central new jersey the new york city boroughs of manhattan brooklyn queens and long island and floridathe bank provides a range of banking services including automated teller machines telephone and internet banking remote deposit capture overdraft facilities drivein and night deposit services and safe deposit facilities the bank also provides certain international banking services to customers including standby letters of credit documentary letters of credit and related products and certain ancillary services such as foreign exchange documentary collections foreign wire transfers and the maintenance of foreign bank accounts are available products and services as well as transaction accounts for nonresident aliens the banks subsidiaries include an insurance agency offering property and casualty life and health insurance an asset management advisor that is a registered investment advisor with securities and exchange commission sec title insurance agencies in new jersey new york and florida subsidiaries that hold maintain and manage investment assets for the bank a subsidiary that owns and services auto loans a subsidiary that specializes in healthcare equipment lending and other commercial equipment leases and a subsidiary that owns and services new york commercial loanscommercial lending segmentthe commercial lending segment includes commercial and industrial loans and commercial real estate loans the company makes commercial loans to small and middle market businesses generally located in the new jersey and new york area as well as florida its commercial loan products include term loans for equipment purchases working capital lines of credit that assist its customers financing of accounts receivable and inventory and commercial mortgages for owner occupied properties the company through its leasing subsidiary highland capital corp provides financing to the medical equipment leasing market the company also offers taxi medallion loans the company originates commercial real estate loans that are primarily secured by multiunit residential property and nonowner occupied commercial industrial and retail property within new jersey new york pennsylvania and florida as of december   the companys commercial and industrial loans totaled approximately  billion as of december   its commercial real estate loans and construction loans totaled  billionconsumer lending segmentthe company offers a range of residential mortgage loans for the purpose of purchasing or refinancing one to fourfamily residential properties the bank is also a servicer of residential mortgage portfolios its other consumer loan portfolio includes direct and indirect automobile loans home equity loans and lines of credit loans secured by the cash surrender value of life insurance and secured and unsecured other consumer loans including credit card loans the company is an auto lender in new jersey new york pennsylvania connecticut delaware and florida offering indirect auto loans secured by either new or used automobiles its wealth management division provides coordinated and integrated delivery of asset management advisory trust general insurance title insurance and trust services its trust services include living and testamentary trusts investment management custodial and escrow services and estate administration primarily to individuals its asset management advisory services include investment services for individuals and small to medium sized businesses trusts and custom tailored investment strategies designed for various types of retirement plans as of december   the companys residential mortgage loans totaled approximately  billion as of december   its other consumer loans totaled  billioninvestment management segmentthe companys investment management segment includes investments in various types of securities as of december   the companys total investment securities and interest bearing deposits with banks were  billion and  million respectively » full overview of vly company address valley national bancorp  valley rdwayne   nj    p f  company web links officers  directors name compensation gerald lipkin  rudy schupp  alan eskow  ira robbins  ronald janis  » more officers  directors valley national bancorp news briefvalley national bancorp announces commencement of series b preferred stock offering jul   briefvalley national bancorp q earnings per share  jul   briefvalley national bancorp to acquire usameribancorp jul   briefvalley national bancorp reports q eps  apr   » more vly news related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsbanks valley national bancorp announces commencement of series b preferred stock offering valley national bancorp announces commencement of series b preferred stock offering news provided by valley national bancorp jul    et share this article wayne nj july   prnewswire  valley national bancorp valley nyse vly today announced that it has commenced a public offering of its noncumulative perpetual preferred stock the preferred stock valley intends to use the net proceeds from this offering for general corporate purposes and investments in valley national bank as regulatory capital the offering is not contingent on the completion of the recently announced acquisition of usameribancorp inc usab and valley cannot provide any assurances that the acquisition will be completed   keefe bruyette  woods a stifel company is acting as bookrunning manager and hovde group llc as comanager for the preferred stock offering the preferred stock will be issued pursuant 